1623
01:51:46,858 --> 01:51:48,056
Querida?

1624
01:52:09,922 --> 01:52:12,413
BEN, MATA-TE A FUMAR.

1625
01:52:12,758 --> 01:52:15,000
PS: QUERO O DIVÓRCIO.

1626
01:52:23,060 --> 01:52:24,388
Gostei de te conhecer.

