1720
01:59:50,037 --> 01:59:51,317
<i>sozinha...</i>

1721
01:59:52,039 --> 01:59:54,364
<i>... a lamber as feridas e a recomeçar,</i>

1722
01:59:56,501 --> 01:59:59,705
<i>libertando-te</i>
<i>para algo melhor no futuro.</i>

1723
02:00:01,882 --> 02:00:04,455
